Softwares Required to Build UI Applications

1. Download and Install the NodeJS.

    Website : https://nodejs.org/en/download/

    file name : node-v6.10.1-x64.msi


2.Download and Install the GIT.

    website : https://git-scm.com/downloads

    file name : Git-2.12.1-64-bit.exe

3.Download WebStrom IDE.

    Website : https://www.jetbrains.com/webstorm/download/#section=windows

    file name : Webstrom-2017.1.exe


4.Install the Bower Plugin

    Open the Terminal in WebStrom IDE.

            (Alt+F12)

    Execute the Following Command.

        npm install -g bower

5. Create the GitHub Account.

    Website : https://github.com/join





































































